Change is good ! I’ve contemplated for a while getting another dog (preferably a pit) but kept worrying, how Momo would feel, do I have time for 2, how they gonna tear stuff up etc 

then just did what I said wanted and decided to HANDLE ANYTHING THAT COMES WITH IT, so the opportunity presented itself (thanks @fairelyseog 🙏🏽 ) so I stepped out on faith , and added another to the family, y’all say hello to miss #Grateful .

 I believe she’s a bull terrier/pit mix. She’s 1 and  some change has puppy dog energy, is a lover girl , loves to cuddle, she’s house trained , happy all the time and over all good dog! Her and momo coo as u can see . And she’s increased my happiness the lil less then week I’ve had her !  Happy I went with intuition  and moved forward ! Expect to see her in my story here on out ! ❤️
